text: Ra usale samudrala'i pani timro adhinama garyo jasabata taja masu khana saka ra tyasabata gahana (ityadi) nikala jasala'i timile laga'umchaum ra timile dekhchau ki dungaharule samudrama pani panchya'umdai agadi badhchan ra yasa karana pani taki timile allahako krpale jivika khojna saka ra jasabata sambhava cha timi usaprati abhara prakata gara
